Package cross.datastructures.tuple

Class Summary
Tuple2D<T,U> Class representing a tuple of two elements with Types T and U.
Tuple2DD Typed specialization of Tuple2D for Double, providing additional methods for arithmetic with Tuple2DD.
Tuple2DDoubleComp Comparator which can be used to sort collections of Tuple2D based on the first element of the tuple.
Tuple2DF Typed specialization of Tuple2D for Float, providing additional methods for arithmetic with Tuple2DF.
Tuple2DI Typed specialization of Tuple2D for Integer.
TupleND<T extends Serializable> Abstract class for N-Tuples of type T, providing different utility methods, to return all non-identical pairs (Ai,Aj), i!
